  "body": "<!-- Please only use this template for submitting enhancement requests -->\r\n\r\n**What would you like to be added**:\r\nAdd an external MetaFactory that allows for serializing multiple YAML (or JSON) files in kubeadm. The logic of marshalling YAML should be factored out from `cmd/kubeadm/app/util/marshal` to `staging/src/k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/serializer/`.\r\n\r\n**Why is this needed**:\r\nThis will allow processing component configs containing multiple documents per file. Additionally, an out-of-tree library would allow sharing this functionality with other components.",
